      "abbreviation": "PX100101",
      "description": "The female participant uses the Tanner staging drawings to self-assess her breast development and pubertal hair.",
      "domain": "Puberty & Development",
      "citation": "Avon Longitudinal Study of Parents and Children (ALSPAC), Growing and Changing (8), Female Teenage Questionnaire - 175 - 204 Months. As implemented in: PhenX Toolkit. Assessment of Pubertal Development - Teenage Female. https://www.phenxtoolkit.org/protocols/view/100101",
